#BackgroundColor allows you to set any bg color for a LABEL
<BackgroundColor@Widget>
    background_color: 1, 1, 1, 1
    canvas.before:
        Color:
            rgba: root.background_color
        Rectangle:
            size: self.size
            pos: self.pos

<BackgroundLabel@Label+BackgroundColor>
    background_color: 0, 0, 0, 0
#Now use BackgroundLabel in place of Label